题。日本大量自来水管道检出致癌物"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pica.zhimg.com/80/v2-0da075d2e8c7a95492f91ec616185ad5_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "18 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/5559507592"}}, "attached_info": "CkEIwbC69Lrduq4TEAMaCTExMjA4ODQyMCD/5Kq6BjAAOL0DQAlyCjU1NTk1MDc1OTJ4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "10_1733018906.135345", "card_id": "Q_3462766462", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 28}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "炖肉时总会放各种香料，这些香料对肉的口味口感会有什么影响？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-b460ac25b51cc92ac1eaf8353dbe24c0_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "16 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/3462766462"}}, "attached_info": "CkEIwbC69Lrduq4TEAMaCTExMTY2OTMzNSD1orK5BjAAOIUBQApyCjM0NjI3NjY0NjJ4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "11_1733018906.135580", "card_id": "Q_5446091525", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 34}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "小草包横扫 Doinb 队后发朋友圈锐评「比打单简单」，Doinb 还有机会复出吗？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "[图片]"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-f0f47b147a8d2612ad7d592df9061c25_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "3.5 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/5446091525"}}, "attached